{"tid":2139432,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"青衣梁植偉紀念中學被掟汽油彈　3 人涉縱火刑毀等被捕　兩人是該校學生　警：疑犯希望學校罷課","createTime":"2020-08-04T09:24:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T13:18:16.000Z","uid":207846,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c9fa0f7e93774a1bbb40cdb494d341515f41b55e","tid":2139432,"uid":207846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T09:24:04.000Z","msg":"位於青衣長康邨的樂善堂梁植偉紀念中學，分別於今年 5 月及 7 月，校門被破壞及掟汽油彈， 警方今（4 日）表示，案發至今拘捕 3 名年齡介乎 16 至 23 歲男子，其中兩名是該校學生，另一名是畢業生，他們涉嫌縱火、刑事毀壞和藏有攻擊性武器等被捕；警方經調查後相信 3 人希望透過破壞校門，以達致罷課目的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E9%9D%92%E8%A1%A3%E6%A2%81%E6%A4%8D%E5%81%89%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%9F%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88-3-%E4%BA%BA%E6%B6%89%E7%B8%B1%E7%81%AB%E5%88%91%E6%AF%80%E7%AD%89%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E5%85%A9%E4%BA%BA%E6%98%AF%E8%A9%B2%E6%A0%A1%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F-%E8%AD%A6-%E7%96%91%E7%8A%AF%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1%E7%BD%B7%E8%AA%B2/?fbclid=IwAR37pRZvXMd5j2_Hy3ttepctJ2HX54fGQHG7D_A_k_gfRbnh-FMlifIZ8gs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E9%259D%2592%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%25A4%258D%25E5%2581%2589%25E7%25B4%2580%25E5%25BF%25B5%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%259F%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BD%2588-3-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B6%2589%25E7%25B8%25B1%25E7%2581%25AB%25E5%2588%2591%25E6%25AF%2580%25E7%25AD%2589%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2598%25AF%25E8%25A9%25B2%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F-%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E7%2596%2591%25E7%258A%25AF%25E5%25B8%258C%25E6%259C%259B%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E7%25BD%25B7%25E8%25AA%25B2%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR37pRZvXMd5j2_Hy3ttepctJ2HX54fGQHG7D_A_k_gfRbnh-FMlifIZ8gs&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd%2FY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=a65df65c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E9%259D%2592%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E6%25A